image, A calm panoramic view of Nykarleby with a winding river, wooden town buildings, and open fields under late-summer light.
Nykarleby lies quiet in the late summer of 1808. The river bends slowly past the town, fields stand undisturbed, and no sign yet reveals that war is drawing near.
